{"tid":2488683,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"AKB/OUC48本家討論區#16 驅逐原神還我本家地標","createTime":"2021-04-14T11:37:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T11:50:18.000Z","uid":186334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5890e59f8d56b479da0f33e48b1d5cd1dc6a75c7","tid":2488683,"uid":186334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:37:38.000Z","msg":"暨AKB48本家討論區#69<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW4Uo2sfr98LztTRUqLfjTNmesAFc8ZSbUiDJZWk2TcLL?filename=R8pt2yL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR8pt2yL.jpg&h=ea24d506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQzCFyTBNgVxoif5pSWJCYGX3LUoEzZGdndAtNfjsGsc9?filename=M14RfUm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM14RfUm.jpg&h=e13dab22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWdzHB5YSNrXWaSWFPBdB12tva36qYxmH3Er5tn7NtE1y?filename=uJCLkks.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuJCLkks.jpg&h=f2e106d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然最近推得勁慢,但本區宗旨係悠閒既聚腳點,唔求一個月爆po,但求大家得閒貼下圖吹兩句就好,歡迎各路人馬加入本家大家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n蒙大家錯愛,本PO可以開到68,想再次重申開番本家PO既原意係希望俾各位本家飯有個集中地吹奏自己個推,無論貼圖又好、放mb活動既情報上黎又好、打機過唔到、番工辛苦吐苦水,甚至想講自己同MB已經有默契,心入面有各自既位置都無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明白到現今世代好多48飯都係各團互走,亦唔介意大家偶爾貼下其他分團既成員介紹俾其他會員知道,總之唔好貼到或宣傳到呢度變左100%既分團討論區就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實呢邊規矩好簡單:<br />\n1. 唔明或有野想知可以問其他巴打或google。<br />\n2. 討論過程實有爭論或嘈交,基本上唔好人身攻擊就得。<br />\n3. 明白到理論上<span class=\"x-small\"><span class=\"navy\">除左完美既奈奈外</span></span>無一個MB係完美既,黑還黑、恥笑還恥笑,唔好太過分傷到成員既飯既感情就好了。<br />\n4. 8仔算唔算本家?<del>自古以來就係本家神聖不可分割既一部份</del>有人算有人唔算,呢邊無咩所謂都歡迎討論同吹奏。<br />\n5. 本PO歡迎mb生日圖海洗1001,唔好分開2日洗就ok。<br />\n6. 萬一真係咁唔好彩有會員唔小心自爆左,麻煩大家唔好引用落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7. 如果係吹奏46團或想撩人過檔請麻煩番去46團既相關po,有緣既話巴打們自然會過去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n8. 通常啲會員掛住某mb神id但吹奏既永遠都係第二個<br />\n9. 本家on9會見盡好多人真係癈到<br />\n10. 世界仔剩係反牙達<br />\n11. 2020已經夠可怕,但2021......<br />\n12. 本家區三大黨派:小栗派(<del>並唔存在</del>)&amp;柏木軍＆瑞葵組<del>都市傳說</del><del>,話說話天下三分但得柏木同完美奈奈生日有圖海爆po</del><br />\n13. MARY:好想一生一世守護__ __BB豬(每星期更新)<br />\n14. 本家全純血出既單曲可能會俾支那武漢肺炎攪到有機會出到<br />\n15. 支那狗還我實體握手會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n16. 連NGT都仲可以出到5單<br />\n17. 已經消失的10專<br />\n18. 以為睇垃圾泡狗就好似高人一等咁,得喇得喇,知啦知啦,叻啦叻啦,行開啲啦,屌你老母<br />\n19. 世界大事：11月7日係完美既奈奈同轆轆既生日<br />\n20. 本家被支那武漢肺炎害慘既新希望:<del>萌夏</del>豬琪BB<br />\n一切既知識:<br />\n<a href=\"http://google.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoogle.com&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1Tvbkzvuu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=9b45e3ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://google.com</a><br />\n<br />\n特別鳴謝會然I am Mary：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1qFHsr_JzhWwiRAkGOCu0185Od67ERVVM63E1bj309o4/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1qFHsr_JzhWwiRAkGOCu0185Od67ERVVM63E1bj309o4%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1Tvbkzvuu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=c60d70fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1qFHsr_JzhWwiRAkGOCu0185Od67ERVVM63E1bj309o4/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n握手流程攻略 KEEP住UPDATE<br />\n<br />\n其他諗到再加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8286d5c5dfce71c1ee19d845db7a7b5863d1621","tid":2488683,"uid":186334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T11:38:21.000Z","msg":"<del>反清復明</del>俾番轆轆個肚臍我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4d1b